des:
Listen to this story with a timeless lesson. 
Ameera revisits the Swede Hollow in a dream, but waking up to a world of materialism symbolized by birthday gifts, she inquires on to the true reality, the world of materialism she lives in or her dreams, in the Swede Hollow, an off grid living of high thinking, warmth and simplicity, essentially minimalism.
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
